{
  "text": "Similarly, Dr. Warshaw's group from the Massachusetts General Hospital (MGH) has also recommended observation for selected patients with cystic lesions of the pancreas. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Fernandez-del Castillo et al reported on 212 patients evaluated at the MGH for a cystic lesion of the pancreas over a 5-year time period.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "14717035",
    "[CITATION_2]": "22126551"
